title: Oh Baby! There’s a New Teether in Town – The Silli Chews™ Baby Teethers!
text:
NEWS , PRODUCT PROMOTIONS This slideshow requires JavaScript. 
Conceptualized and designed by Moms, Silli Chews™ is a collection of handmade, soft, silicone textured teethers using exclusive patented process. Designed for ages three months and up, Silli Chews™ are perfect for baby’s sensitive gums. The teether can also be chilled for added relief. 
Silli Chews™ feature playful designs in vibrant, eye- catching colors. The multidimensional teethers in this adorable collection include colorful bugs called Silli Bugs , Mommy/Daddy and Baby Animal sets called Silli Families and everyday objects babies love to grab called Silli Things . 
Fun Zone Inc. , creator of the Silli Chews™ collection, will partner with Bottle Pets for nationwide distribution. Silli Chews™ will debut at the ABC Kids Expo October 18th through the 21st at the Las Vegas Convention Center in Bottle Pets booth #1441, South Hall level 1. 
Silli Chews™ meet or exceed all FDA, CPSIA and ASTM standards. The teethers are made of 100% food grade silicone and are free of BPA, PVC, and Phthalates. Easy to clean and dishwasher safe, Silli Chews™ are odorless and tasteless. 
Silli Chews™ are designed to simultaneously soothe and amuse baby while easing mommy and daddy’s worried mind, expected on store shelves in early 2016. MSRP: $22 for a set of two.
